001package edu.cnm.deepdive.tetris.model.pojo;
002
003import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
004import androidx.room.DatabaseView;
005import java.time.Instant;
006
007@DatabaseView(
008    viewName = "user_score",
009    value = "SELECT s.player_id,\n"
010        + "       u.display_name,\n"
011        + "       s.value,\n"
012        + "       s.rows_removed,\n"
013        + "       s.created\n"
014        + "FROM user AS u\n"
015        + "         JOIN score AS s ON u.user_id = s.player_id"
016)
017public class UserScore {
018
019  @ColumnInfo(name = "player_id")
020  private long playerId;
021
022  @ColumnInfo(name = "display_name")
023  private String displayName;
024
025  private long value;
026
027  @ColumnInfo(name = "rows_removed")
028  private int rowsRemoved;
029
030  private Instant created;
031
032  public long getPlayerId() {
033    return playerId;
034  }
035
036  public void setPlayerId(long playerId) {
037    this.playerId = playerId;
038  }
039
040  public String getDisplayName() {
041    return displayName;
042  }
043
044  public void setDisplayName(String displayName) {
045    this.displayName = displayName;
046  }
047
048  public long getValue() {
049    return value;
050  }
051
052  public void setValue(long value) {
053    this.value = value;
054  }
055
056  public int getRowsRemoved() {
057    return rowsRemoved;
058  }
059
060  public void setRowsRemoved(int rowsRemoved) {
061    this.rowsRemoved = rowsRemoved;
062  }
063
064  public Instant getCreated() {
065    return created;
066  }
067
068  public void setCreated(Instant created) {
069    this.created = created;
070  }
071}
